<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5487561>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1–9. Alepia iy sp. nov. 1. Head with complete palpus. 2. Head, anterior view. 3. Head, posterior view. 4. Flagellomeres I–XIV. 5. Flagellomeres XI–XIV in detail. 6. Wing. Fig. 7–9. Male terminalia. 7. Lateral view. 8. Detail of hypandrium, gonocoxite, gonostylus and aedeagus, lateral view. 9. Detail of hypandrium, gonocoxite, gonostylus, aedeagal sheath and aedeagus, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5487561/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

